        {
          "id": "d597537603ef_1",
          "href": null,
          "name": "f80b",
          "text": "Goethe Institute Webinar 1 — Daniel C. Wahl visit to Brazil",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "H4"
        },
        {
          "id": "d597537603ef_2",
          "href": null,
          "name": "b5f9",
          "text": "Earlier this year — in March — I spent 12 very intense days in Brazil to offer a few talks, workshops and a four day immersive to celebrate that Editora Bambual had translated my book, Designing Regenerative Cultures, into Brazilian Portuguese. I had the good fortune of having Flávia Vivacqua and Taisa Mattos take on the job of organising the whole trip for me. I am deeply grateful to both of them!",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 216,
              "href": "https://bambualeditora.com.br/p/design-de-culturas-regenerativas/",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 185,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "d597537603ef_3",
          "href": null,
          "name": "181a",
          "text": "Together with Tatyana Lorenz of the Goethe Institute Sao Paulo we co-created the ‘Regenerative Design Cycle’ which started with two webinars before the visit. Below is the recording of the first of them, recorded in January 2019. The webinar was live with simultaneous translation to Portuguese and what’s more simultaneous subtitling! ( There are two short glitches in the sound — only a few seconds!)",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "d597537603ef_4",
          "href": null,
          "name": "f252",
          "text": "Design Regenerativo\ndedica-se há mais de 20 anos aos estudos da natureza e dos sistemas ecológicos. Educador e consultor para organizações…www.designregenerativo.org",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": {
            "href": "https://www.designregenerativo.org",
            "thumbnailImageId": "0*ZnlAheWS-rLCVMEW",
            "mediaResourceId": "ae8be7d2c8632c66189b757f2e15268b"
          },
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 165,
              "href": "https://www.designregenerativo.org",
              "rel": "",
